---
// Services section inspired by Livefront's service offerings
---

<section id="services" class="py-24 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight tracking-tight"
      >
        What I bring to your team
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
      >
        Full-stack expertise across modern technologies, with a focus on scalable architecture, user
        experience, and delivering products that make a real impact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-12 mb-20">
      <!-- Frontend Development -->
      <div
        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-10 shadow-soft hover:shadow-elevated border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-soft group-hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
              Frontend Development
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Building modern, responsive interfaces with React, TypeScript, and Next.js. Focused on
              performance, accessibility, and exceptional user experiences.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-800 dark:text-primary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >React</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-800 dark:text-primary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >TypeScript</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-800 dark:text-primary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Next.js</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-800 dark:text-primary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Tailwind CSS</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Backend Development -->
      <div
        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-10 shadow-soft hover:shadow-elevated border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-soft group-hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-400"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
              Backend Development
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Designing scalable APIs and data architectures. Experience with Ruby on Rails,
              Node.js, Python, and cloud platforms for high-traffic applications.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Ruby on Rails</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Node.js</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Python</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >PostgreSQL</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >AWS</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- System Architecture -->
      <div
        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-10 shadow-soft hover:shadow-elevated border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-100 dark:bg-accent-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-soft group-hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
              System Architecture
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Designing resilient systems that scale. Experience with CI/CD pipelines, automated
              testing, and cloud infrastructure for healthcare and government applications.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-100 dark:bg-accent-900 text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Jenkins</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-100 dark:bg-accent-900 text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Playwright</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-100 dark:bg-accent-900 text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >CI/CD</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-100 dark:bg-accent-900 text-accent-800 dark:text-accent-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >AWS</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product Strategy -->
      <div
        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-10 shadow-soft hover:shadow-elevated border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-soft group-hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-7 h-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
              Product Strategy
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Collaborating with cross-functional teams including UX researchers, policy experts,
              and support staff to build accessible, user-centered healthcare applications.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Agile</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >WCAG Compliance</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Production Support</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Healthcare Technology</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Impact Statement -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        I bring technical excellence and product thinking together to build solutions that don't
        just work—they make a meaningful impact for users and businesses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Staggered animation for service cards */
  .grid > div:nth-child(1) {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.6s ease-out 0.1s both;
  }
  .grid > div:nth-child(2) {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }
  .grid > div:nth-child(3) {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.6s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }
  .grid > div:nth-child(4) {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.6s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
